## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Option 1: Direct Usage
1. Download all files (index.html, styles.css, script.js)
2. Keep all files in the same folder
3. Open `index.html` in your web browser
4. That's it! Your website is ready

### Option 2: GitHub Deployment
1. Create a new repository on GitHub
2. Upload all three files to the repository
3. Go to Settings â†’ Pages
4. Select main branch as source
5. Your site will be live at: `https://yourusername.github.io/repository-name`

### Option 3: Local Server
```bash
# Using Python 3
python -m http.server 8000

# Using Node.js (with http-server)
npx http-server

# Then open: http://localhost:8000
```

## ğŸ“ Customization Guide

### Changing Colors
Edit the CSS variables in `styles.css`:
```css
:root {
    --primary-color: #6366f1;    /* Main brand color */
    --secondary-color: #8b5cf6;  /* Secondary accent */
    --accent-color: #ec4899;      /* Highlight color */
}
```

### Updating Content
- **Company Name**: Search and replace "Subrata AI" in `index.html`
- **Services**: Edit the service cards in the services section
- **Contact Info**: Update email, phone, address in the contact section

### Adding New Sections
1. Add HTML structure in `index.html`
2. Style it in `styles.css`
3. Add interactions in `script.js` if needed

